<p>
<lb n="1"/>śrī <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śākābdē nidhiśailabhānugaṇitē <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="2"/>gīṣpativāsarē phaṇitithau śrīsiṁhaśailēsituḥ <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="3"/>kasya duhitā svābhīṣṭapuṇyāptayē tallammā guṇa<unclear>śā</unclear>linī pratidi
<lb n="4" break="no"/>naṁ prādāt prasūnasrajaṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śakavarṣaṁbulu 1279 gunēṁṭi mā
<lb n="5" break="no"/>rggaśira śukla paṁcamiyu guruvāramunāṁḍu mādhavanā
<lb n="6" break="no"/>yakuni kūṁtuṟu tallamma tanaku puṇyamugānu
<lb n="7"/>śrīnarasiṁhanāthunikini nityamunnu Oka tirumāla cātiṁpanu si
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ṁhagirināyaka dēvunāyakuniki gaṁḍamāḍalu padi Icci
<lb n="9"/>kuṁcannaḍḍaprasādamu ṭhāvupaṭṭi <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Ī prasādamunu ciṁgunāya
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ka gōpināthuni<unclear>cē</unclear>ta koni puṣpavāṭika gaṭṭu Okaṭinni Ī dēvunā
<lb n="11" break="no"/>yuni kiccenu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> vīru nityamunnu Ātupāśi Āṟu māḷlu peṭṭaṁgalaru Ī dha
<lb n="12" break="no"/>rmmu śrīvaiṣṇava rakṣa <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śatruṇāpi kutō dharmaḥ pālanīyō manīṣibhiḥ
<lb n="13"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> śatrusyāddharma <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> syacit <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrīśrīśrī 
